company_name: BASSUMER FRISCHEI HEINRICH TIEMANN GMBH & CO. EIERHANDEL-KOMMANDITGESELLSCHAFT
information: The company BASSUMER FRISCHEI HEINRICH TIEMANN GMBH & CO. EIERHANDEL-KOMMANDITGESELLSCHAFT, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1979, which operates in the Eggs industry. It is based in Bassum, Germany.
